le%2C%20Temu%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20free%20iPhone%20app%20in%20the%20US%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Australia%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20has%20Temu%20been%20such%20a%20massive%20success%3F%20It's%20safe%20to%20say%20the%20platform%20has%20some%20winning%20strategies%20that%20keep%20consumers%20coming%20back.%20But%20beyond%20that%2C%20similar%20to%20other%20e-commerce%20platforms%2C%20using%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20risk-%20or%20guilt-free.%20Here%20are%20some%20things%20to%20consider%20if%20you're%20thinking%20of%20giving%20it%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20Temu's%20secrets%20to%20success%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Australians%20might%20associate%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20in%20China%E2%80%9D%20with%20cheap%20price%20tags%20and%20low%20quality.%20However%2C%20Temu's%20consumers%20are%20beginning%20to%20view%20it%20as%20offering%20affordable%20products%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-08-29%2Ftemu-may-save-china-status-as-world-factory-amid-deflation%2F102724900%5C%22%3Edo%20not%20necessarily%20compromise%20on%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%2010-20%20products%20will%20only%20set%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business2community.com%2Ftech-news%2Fspending-on-temu-continues-to-skyrocket-beating-out-shein-by-20-in-may-02707455%5C%22%3Eyou%20back%20US%2420-30%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemu%20claims%20it%20can%20offer%20these%20prices%20as%20a%20result%20of%20cutting%20out%20the%20middlemen%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%20While%20the%20manufacturers%20provide%20the%20product%20details%20and%20the%20products%20themselves%2C%20Temu%20handles%20everything%20else%20%E2%80%93%20from%20customs%20processing%20to%20international%20shipping.%20This%20streamlining%20helps%20reduce%20unit%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20achieving%20such%20value%20doesn't%20come%20without%20a%20cost.%20Concerns%20are%20rising%20that%20Temu%20and%20its%20suppliers%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Ftemu-is-losing-millions-of-dollars-to-send-you-cheap-socks%5C%22%3Eoperating%20at%20a%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it's%20common%20for%20startups%20to%20experience%20negative%20cash%20flow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F309770487_Score_model_for_technology_appraisal_of_Bulgarian_start-ups%5C%22%3Ein%20their%20initial%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20heavy%20marketing%20investments%2C%20including%20offers%20of%20competitive%20prices%20and%20marketing%20campaigns%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20which%20is%20done%20to%20build%20brand%20awareness%20and%20gain%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20true%20in%20the%20fast-paced%20e-commerce%20sector%2C%20where%20success%20and%20failure%20happen%20swiftly.%20Temu%20and%20its%20suppliers%2C%20who%20are%20mainly%20from%20Temu's%20sister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Ftemu-taps-on-sister-e-commerce-platform-supply-chain-to-offer-irresistible-prices-301623014.html%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20platform%20Pinduoduo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20likely%20aware%20of%20this%20dynamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20An%20effective%20marketing%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20e-commerce%20platforms%20that%20focus%20on%20functional%20benefits%20such%20as%20saving%20money%2C%20Temu%20caters%20to%20consumers'%20emotional%20needs.%20It%20overlays%20the%20shopping%20experience%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cshopping%20like%20a%20billionaire%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20which%20also%20aligns%20with%20its%20value-based%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemu%20entered%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20consumers%20were%20grappling%20with%20global%20inflation%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Cvalue%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20first%20month%20after%20its%20launch%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Temu%20invested%20some%20US%24200%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatalk.nl%2Ftemu-update-june-2023-part-1-from-0-to-400-million-monthly-gmv-in-8-months%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20advertising%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20planned%20a%20US%242%20billion%20budget%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40keshi201109%2Fwhat-did-temu-do-right-6b31d6e2372f%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20China's%20leadership%20in%20live-streaming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feprints.qut.edu.au%2F235249%2F%5C%22%3Einfluencer%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Temu%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftalkleisure.com%2Fhow-to-become-a-temu-influencer%2F%23Does_Temu_Use_Influencer_Marketing%5C%22%3Erecruiting%20social%20media%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggesting%20it%20might%20leverage%20its%20Chinese%20expertise%20to%20explore%20a%20social-commerce%20strategy.%20Social%20commerce%20harnesses%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfriendship%E2%80%9D%20conveyed%20by%20influencers%2C%20making%20the%20online%20shopping%20experience%20more%20engaging%20and%20product%20recommendations%20more%20convincing.%20It%20also%20works%20especially%20well%20with%20sales%20promotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESales%20promotion%20tactics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Temu%20employs%20common%20sales%20tactics%20seen%20on%20other%20e-commerce%20platforms%2C%20it%20uses%20what%20is%20arguably%20the%20broadest%20array%20of%20these%20techniques.%20Here%20are%20just%20some%20examples%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGamified%20experiences.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Gamified%20advertising%20hinges%20on%20two%20core%20elements%3A%20challenge%20and%20reward.%20Interacting%20with%20Temu's%20spinning%20wheel%20is%20a%20minor%20challenge%2C%20but%20the%20substantial%20discount%20offered%20is%20a%20major%20reward.%20Such%20%E2%80%9Cgames%E2%80%9D%20create%20the%20illusion%20of%20getting%20lucky%2C%20and%20therefore%20generate%20positive%20emotions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feprints.qut.edu.au%2F242174%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20reward%20gives%20them%20an%20incentive%20to%20engage%20more%20seriously%20with%20their%20browsing%2C%20increasing%20the%20likelihood%20of%20spending.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELightning%20deals%20and%20limited-time%20offers.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20commonly%20used%20promotion%20tactic%20involves%20creating%20the%20illusion%20of%20scarcity%20through%20supposedly%20%E2%80%9Cexclusive%E2%80%9D%20offers%20that%20are%20time-sensitive%20and%20won't%20come%20by%20again.%20This%20can%20trigger%20a%20fear%20of%20missing%20out%20in%20consumers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscounts%20and%20free%20shipping%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Offering%20simple%20price%20reductions%20and%20very%20affordable%20sales%20is%20a%20time-honoured%20way%20of%20securing%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base.%20In%20addition%2C%20Temu%20has%20the%20allure%20of%20offering%20free%20shipping%20on%20orders%20with%20a%20very%20low%20minimum%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoyalty%20program%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Consumers%20can%20opt%20in%20to%20Temu's%20marketing%20emails%20in%20exchange%20for%20receiving%20more%20promotional%20content%2C%20including%20email-only%20promotions.%20E-commerce%20companies%20often%20have%20access%20to%20your%20personal%20information%20(such%20as%20your%20name%2C%20address%2C%20age%20and%20phone%20number)%20and%20behavioural%20data%20(such%20as%20from%20your%20search%20history%20and%20online%20sessions).%20With%20this%20data%2C%20the%20company%20can%20build%20your%20user%20profile%20and%20target%20you%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs11747-020-00719-1%5C%22%3Epersonalised%20promotions%20and%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20encourage%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESearch%20engine%20marketing.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20consumers%20will%20see%20Temu%20ads%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20search%20results%20on%20Google%20(in%20the%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Csponsored%E2%80%9D%20posts)%20when%20they%20search%20for%20a%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20AI-powered%20promotional%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Temu's%20sister%20company%20operating%20in%20China%2C%20Pinduoduo%2C%20is%20renowned%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fa16z.com%2F2023%2F01%2F18%2Fwhat-is-temu%2F%5C%22%3EAI-driven%20recommendation%3C%2Fa%3E%20system.%20It's%20likely%20Temu%20uses%20similar%20AI%20algorithms%2C%20drawing%20on%20users'%20browsing%20and%20purchase%20history%20to%20provide%20personalised%20recommendations%20(a%20practice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2Fartificial-intelligence-video-ads-augmented-reality%2F%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20partakes%20in).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EDefending%20against%20manipulation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemu's%20greatest%20benefit%20to%20consumers%20lies%20in%20its%20offer%20of%20value.%20It%20may%20still%20have%20lower-quality%20items%2C%20but%20this%20is%20common%20among%20all%20e-commerce%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Temu's%20business%20model%20is%20built%20around%20emphasising%20top-selling%20products%2C%20which%20helps%20filter%20out%20low-quality%20products.%20Its%2090-day%20free%20return%20policy%20further%20acts%20as%20a%20buffer%20for%20unsatisfactory%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20Temu's%20value-oriented%20approach%20may%20not%20be%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20consumers%20on%20all%20fronts.%20Exposed%20to%20such%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20marketing%20tactics%2C%20users%20might%20become%20more%20prone%20to%20overconsumption%20%E2%80%93%20which%20leads%20to%20environmental%20waste%20and%20post-purchase%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20considering%20your%20actual%20needs%20before%20using%20an%20e-commerce%20platform%20such%20as%20Temu.%20You%20should%20also%20familiarise%20yourself%20with%20the%20sales%20promotion%20tactics%20being%20used.%20Research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1002%2Fmar.21266%5C%22%3Esuggests%3C%2Fa%3E%20understanding%20these%20tactics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20advertisers'%20intentions%2C%20can%20even%20empower%20young%20children%20to%20be%20sceptical%20and%20form%20a%20cognitive%20defence%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20in%20light%20of%20Temu's%20gamified%20advertising%20strategy%2C%20consumers%20ought%20to%20temper%20their%20enthusiasm%20for%20rewards.%20Moving%20forward%2C%20one%20useful%20approach%20may%20be%20for%20schools%20and%20governments%20to%20introduce%20educational%20programs%20or%20social%20marketing%20campaigns%20that%20teach%20advertising%20tactics%2C%20and%20recommend%20coping%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETemu%20didn't%20respond%20to%20The%20Conversation's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cimg%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22no-referrer-when-downgrade%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F212463%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fshasha-wang-994374%5C%22%3EShasha%20Wang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Senior%20lecturer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fqueensland-university-of-technology-847%5C%22%3EQueensland%20University%20of%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fxiaoling-guo-1467965%5C%22%3EXiaoling%20Guo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fthe-university-of-western-australia-1067%5C%22%3EThe%20University%20of%20Western%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republishe