0Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20for%20upholding%20dynastic%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20465px)%2085vw%2C%20465px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22465%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n.jpeg%20890w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21161801%2F299513751_611069033716015_2467393198214616918_n-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22465%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEdappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FEdappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20262%20eminent%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20former%20high%20court%20judges%20and%20bureaucrats%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20Tuesday%20urging%20him%20to%20take%20note%20of%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20speech%20calling%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20concern%20over%20the%20growing%20incidents%20of%20hate%20speeches%2C%20the%20bureaucrats%20urged%20the%20apex%20court%20to%20take%20a%20suo%20moto%20notice%20of%20contempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20cases%20should%20be%20suo%20moto%20registered%20and%20the%20offenders%20should%20be%20proceeded%20against%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%20Any%20hesitation%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20directions%20would%20be%20viewed%20as%20contempt%20of%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20state