%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fimage-feature%2Fgoddard%2F2023%2Fnasa-s-lro-observes-chandrayaan-3-landing-site%5C%22%3ENASA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20LRO%20camera%20acquired%20an%20oblique%20view%20(42-degree%20slew%20angle)%20of%20the%20lander%20four%20days%20later.%20The%20bright%20halo%20around%20the%20vehicle%20resulted%20from%20the%20rocket%20plume%20interacting%20with%20the%20fine-grained%20regolith%20(soil).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fmysterious-earth-like-planet-hiding-in-the-solar-system-says-study-4361091%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Mysterious%20Earth-Like%20Planet%20Hiding%20In%20The%20Solar%20System%2C%20Says%20Study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELRO%20is%20managed%20by%20NASA's%20Goddard%20Space%20Flight%20Center%20in%20Greenbelt%2C%20Maryland%2C%20for%20the%20Science%20Mission%20Directorate%20at%20the%20agency's%20headquarters%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20organisation%20on%20Tuesday%20put%20out%20a%203-dimensional%20'anaglyph'%20image%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20Vikram%20lander%20from%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20anaglyph%20presented%20here%20is%20created%20using%20NavCam%20stereo%20images%2C%20which%20consist%20of%20both%20a%20left%20and%20right%20image%20captured%20onboard%20the%20Pragyan%20Rover%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20space%20agency%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnaglyph%20is%20a%20simple%20visualization%20of%20the%20object%20or%20terrain%20in%20three%20dimensions%20from%20stereo%20or%20multi-view%20images.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Anaglyph%20presented%20here%20is%20created%20using%20NavCam%20Stereo%20Images%2C%20which%20consist%20of%20both%20a%20left%20and%20right%20image%20captured%20onboard%20the%20Pragyan%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT8ksnvrovA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FT8ksnvrovA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1699039768053706764%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnaglyph%20is%20a%20simple%20visualization%20of%20an%20object%20or%20terrain%20in%20three%20dimensions%20from%20stereo%20or%20multi-view%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%203-channel%20image%2C%20the%20left%20image%20is%20positioned%20in%20the%20red%20channel%2C%20while%20the%20right%20image%20is%20placed%20in%20the%20blue%20and%20green%20channels%20(creating%20cyan).%20The%20difference%20in%20perspective%20between%20these%20two%20images%20results%20in%20the%20stereo%20effect%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20visual%20impression%20of%20three%20dimensions.%20Red%20and%20cyan%20glasses%20are%20recommended%20for%20viewing%20in%203D%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERed%20and%20cyan%20glasses%20are%20recommended%20for%20viewing%20in%203D.%20NavCam%20was%20developed%20by%20LEOS%2FISRO.%20Data%20processing%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20SAC%2FISRO%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693980600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9shajc98_chandrayaan3-lander-is-in-the-center-of-the-image_625x300_06_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-posts-pic-of-chandrayaan-3-lander-on-moon-clicked-by-its-satellite-4363633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20August%2023%2C%20India%20took%20a%20giant%20leap%20as%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20module%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-posts-pic