atic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103419090%2Cimgsize-72994.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Factors-whove-donned-the-army-uniform%2Fphotostory%2F103419090.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103419090.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BActors%20who've%20donned%20the%20army%20uniform%20%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Caste%20Census%2C%20Privacy%20and%20the%20Control%20of%20Social%20Information%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Annual%20privacy%20conference%20%E2%80%98Privacy%20Supreme%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20was%20a%20discussion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRO3KY9oZCXc%5C%22%3ECaste%2C%20Privacy%20and%20Digital%20Technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Nikita%20Sonavane%20and%20Manoj%20Mitta.%20An%20important%20debate%20considering%20ongoing%20litigation%20around%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20potentially%20violating%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20by%20publishing%20data.%20There%20have%20been%20further%20arguments%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20on%20how%20only%20the%20Centre%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-govt-defensive-over-bihar-caste-survey-changes-affidavit-in-supreme-court%5C%22%3Eallowed%20to%20conduct%20a%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20opening%20up%20questions%20on%20who%20gets%20to%20control%20this%20social%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20the%20census%20has%20been%20contentious%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20how%20the%20colonial%20census%20was%20used%20to%20criminalise%20caste%20groups%20and%20tribes%20in%20India.%20This%20is%20often%20not%20understood%20by%20upper%20caste%20groups.%20As%20Mitta%20noted%2C%20the%20state%20also%20decided%20not%20to%20collect%20the%20economic%20status%20of%20people%20other%20than%20SCs%20and%20STs%20post%20independence.%20The%20caste%20data%20collected%20under%20the%20Socio%20Economic%20Caste%20Census%20of%202011%20carried%20out%20during%20the%20UPA%20regime%20was%20never%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20control%20of%20caste%20data%20suppresses%20the%20narratives%20around%20the%20socio-economic%20status%20of%20various%20caste%20groups%20by%20denying%20them%20information%20about%20themselves.%20By%20carrying%20out%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20set%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3Econversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20rolling%20around%20the%20Brahmanical%20regime%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20caste%20census%20data%20and%20the%20delay%20in%20census%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arguments%20over%20privacy%20violations%20made%20by%20an%20organisation%20Youth%20for%20Equality%20were%20rightfully%20rejected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20allowed%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20exercise%20to%20continue.%20It%20is%20always%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20upper%20caste%20groups%20to%20control%20the%20information%20and%20narratives%20around%20caste%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20major%20state%20censuses%20that%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20post%202011%20have%20been%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20these%20states.%20In%20both%20the%20states%2C%20these%20censuses%20have%20been%20called%20surveys%2C%20Samagra%20Kutumba%20Survey%2FIntensive%20Household%20survey%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Praja%20Sadhikara%20Survey%2FSmart%20Pulse%20Survey%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Both%20the%20survey%E2%80%99s%20were%20linked%20to%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20and%20information%20at%20the%20household%20level%20was%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20that%20these%20states%20have%20published%20in%20terms%20of%20official%20reports%20or%20statistics%20based%20on%20these%20surveys.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Telangana%2C%20an%20obscure%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcrhrdi.gov.in%2Fgroup1-2019%2Fweek2%2F3%2Fsiriki%2F(03)%2520SKS%2520comprehensive%2520ppt.pdf%5C%22%3Epresentation%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Human%20Resources%20Development%20Institute%20of%20Telangana%20gives%20some%20insights%20on%20numbers%20about%20this%20Big%20Data%20exercise.%20The%20Government%20of%20Telangana%20used%20data%20from%20this%20exercise%20to%20determine%20households%20that%20will%20be%20included%20as%20part%20of%20Government%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111205%2FSK-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111205%2FSK-1.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111205%2FSK-1-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENumber%20of%20Caste%20Wise%20Households%20in%20Telangana%2C%20included%20and%20excluded%20for%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20Telangana%20often%20uses%20information%20from%20its%20Intensive%20Household%20Survey%20to%20launch%20new%20schemes%20and%20day%20to%20day%20governance%20activities.%20This%20information%20was%20also%20used%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdalitbandhu.telangana.gov.in%2FHome%2FIndex%5C%22%3EDalit%20Bandhu%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20welfare%20scheme%20targeted%20towards%20the%20marginalised%20caste%20groups%20to%20help%20them%20set%20up%20small%20scale%20businesses.%20While%20the%20state%20has%20been%20contributing%20towards%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20a%20fair%20process%20%E2%80%93%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fprotest-over-bias-in-selection-of-dalit-bandhu-beneficiaries%2Farticle67164956.ece%5C%22%3Eprotests%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20rules%20for%20becoming%20eligible%20for%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20scenarios%20where%20the%20state%20is%20collecting%20caste%20information%2C%20but%20not%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20census.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20land%20registration%20portal%20Dharani%2C%20all%20the%20agriculture%20land%20owners%E2%80%99%20information%20is%20public%20including%20their%20caste%20details.%20A%20statistical%20summary%20of%20land%20ownership%20based%20on%20caste%20groups%20is%20different%20from%20displaying%20the%20caste%20group%20of%20individual%20land%20owners.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20land%20ownership%20has%20historically%20been%20associated%20with%20caste%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111347%2FSK2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22651%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111347%2FSK2.png%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06111347%2FSK2-300x217.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETelangana%E2%80%99s%20Land%20Portal%20Displaying%20Personal%20Details%20Including%20Caste%20of%20Land%20Owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20Aadhaar%20to%20create%20360-degree%20profiles%20with%20State%20Resident%20Data%20Hubs%20has%20helped%20states%20to%20understand%20household%20level%20socio-economic%20status%20that%20they%20use%20in%20governance.%20This%20socio-economic%20profile%20includes%20the%20details%20of%20land%2Fproperty%20ownership%20that%20is%20being%20interlinked%20through%20Aadhaar.%20At%20the%20same%20time%20all%20this%20information%20collected%20through%20the%20state%20surveys%20are%20used%20by%20the%20police%20for%20360%20degree%20policing%20of%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20could%20argue%2C%20every%20resident%E2%80%99s%20360%20profile%20is%20being%20shared%20with%20the%20police%2C%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20rights%20are%20being%20violated.%20But%20the%20cost%20of%20privacy%20violations%20for%20Dalits%20and%20other%20marginalised%20communities%20will%20be%20higher%20because%20of%20the%20historical%20police%20violence%20that%20has%20been%20perpetuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20have%20always%20used%20information%20to%20appease%20different%20communities%20with%20economic%20or%20political%20benefits%20that%20they%20can%20use.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Telangana%2C%20while%20the%20government%20is%20promoting%20various%20forms%20of%20welfare%20for%20Dalits%2C%20it%20is%20also%20opposed%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20Dalit%20politics%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftelangana%2F2023%2Fjan%2F03%2Ftelangana-centre-trying-to-hack-my-phone-state-bsp-chief-2534096.html%5C%22%3Esuppressing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0politicians%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehansindia.com%2Ftelangana%2Fbsp-strongly-condemns-the-arrest-of-its-chief-rsp-815194%5C%22%3ER.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar%20of%20the%20BSP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20is%20power%20and%20people%20in%20power%20are%20able%20to%20access%20information%20about%20the%20population%20to%20control%20them.%20But%20state%20mechanisms%20can%20be%20misused%20to%20control%20information%2C%20by%20not%20being%20transparent%20while%20publishing%20statistics%20and%20or%20by%20unauthorised%20usage%20of%20this%20information%20%E2%80%93%20a%20privacy%20violation.%20This%20also%20creates%20an%20information%20asymmetry%20which%20hides%20caste%20violence%2C%20which%20is%20hard%20to%20document%20but%20often%20visible%20in%20our%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bihar%2C%20Aadhaar-linked%20micro%20data%20of%20the%20census%20can%20still%20be%20potentially%20misused%20for%20electioneering%20by%20select%20political%20parties.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20party%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20current%20YSR%20Congress%20party%20too%20is%20using%20government%20machinery%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20surveys%20which%20are%20not%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20threat%20when%20one%20looks%20into%20how%20data%20and%20a%20census%20can%20harm%20the%20marginalised%20communities%20including%20caste%20groups%2C%20is%20that%20of%20demarcation%20of%20electoral%20constitutes%20that%20is%20upcoming%20through%20delimitation%20post%20census%202021.%20The%20US%20Census%20Bureau%20has%20been%20looking%20towards%20using%20various%20mathematical%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fprograms-surveys%2Fdecennial-census%2Fdecade%