sition%20parties'%20reaction%20and%20if%20the%20government%20is%20going%20to%20reposition%20India%20as%20Bharat%20coinciding%20with%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20when%20you%20say%20Bharat%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20a%20meaning%20and%20understanding%20and%20a%20connotation%20that%20comes%20with%20it%20and%20that%20is%20reflected%20in%20our%20Constitution%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20was%20resorting%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrama%26quot%3B%20just%20because%20they%20got%20together%20and%20called%20their%20bloc%20as%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20strongly%20supported%20the%20move%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20posted%20on%20'X'%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20dinner%20invite%20to%20him%20from%20the%20President%20and%20wrote%20a%20few%20lines%20from%20the%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20should%20have%20happened%20earlier.%20This%20gives%20great%20satisfaction%20to%20the%20mind.%20'Bharat'%20is%20our%20introduction.%20We%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%20The%20President%20has%20given%20priority%20to%20'Bharat'.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20statement%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20colonial%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20made%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20news%20is%20indeed%20true.%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20has%20sent%20out%20an%20invite%20for%20a%20G20%20dinner%20on%20September%209th%20in%20the%20name%20of%20'President%20of%20Bharat'%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20'President%20of%20India'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Article%201%20in%20the%20Constitution%20can%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BBharat%2C%20that%20was%20India%2C%20shall%20be%20a%20Union%20of%20States.%26quot%3B%20But%20now%20even%20this%20%26quot%3BUnion%20of%20States%26quot%3B%20is%20under%20assault%2C