erybody%20is%20coming%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20seriousness.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20different%20points%20of%20time%20in%20G20%20there%20have%20been%20some%20presidents%20or%20prime%20ministers%20who%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20have%20chosen%20not%20to%20come%20themselves%20but%20that%20country%2C%20and%20that%20country's%20position%20is%20obviously%20reflected%20by%20whoever%20is%20the%20representative%20on%20that%20occasion.%20So%2C%20you%20had%20some%20occasions%20where%20you%20had%20a%20president%20or%20two%2C%20sometimes%20three%2C%20who%20have%20not%20themselves%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20sense%20from%20talking%20to%20the%20ministers%2C%20certainly%2C%20and%20I%20know%20the%20Sherpas%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other%2C%20they%20are%20right%20now%20trying%20to%20hammer%20out%20the%20final%20document.%20I%20think%20everybody%20is%20coming%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20seriousness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20was%20asked%20if%20President%20Putin%20and%20President%20Xi%20not%20being%20present%20will%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G20%20Summit%20being%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20think%20it%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20India.%20I.%20I%20think%20whatever%20decision%20they%20make%2C%20they%20would%20know%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20in%20response%20to%20another%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20It%20gave%20no%20reason%20for%20Xi%20Jinping's%20absence%20from%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%2C%20in%20a%20telephone%20conversation%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20month%2C%20had%20conveyed%20his%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20S