20preventive%20measures%20are%20not%20taken%20up%20soon%2C%20doctors%20have%20warned.%20The%20cramped%20spaces%20where%20people%20are%20living%2C%20and%20not-so-good%20water%20and%20sanitation%20facilities%2C%20may%20aid%20these%20outbreaks%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20Imphal%2C%20Dr%20M.%20Nara%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20health%20minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20worried%20%E2%80%93%20epidemics%20may%20break%20out%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20dengue%20and%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20because%20the%20season%20is%20such%20and%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20preventive%20measures%20being%20taken%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Dr%20Nara%20Singh%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20an%20association%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idpd.org%2FHome%2FIndex%5C%22%3EIndian%20Doctors%20for%20Peace%20and%20Development%20(IDPD)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20IDPD%20members%20from%20outside%20Manipur%20also%20visited%20the%20state%20on%20September%201%20and%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20more%20than%2060%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20camps%20without%20much%20proper%20arrangement%20and%20therefore%20they%20are%20susceptible%20to%20all%20these%20infections%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Nara%20Singh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20already%20there%20are%20some%20reports%20of%20malaria%20cases%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20entered%20its%20fifth%20month%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Manglem%20Singh%2C%20another%20IDPD%20member%20based%20in%20Imphal%2C%20said%20that%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20the%20camps%20have%20piped%20water%20supply.%20The%20rest%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20potable%20water%20which%20is%20supplied%20through%20tankers.%20Not%20only%20can%20the%20supply%20be%20erratic%20due%20to%20blockades%2C%20but%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20ensure%20the%20quality%20of%20drinking%20water%20being%20supplied%20like%20this.%20Dr%20Manglem%20Singh%20is%20a%20retired%20medical%20officer%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoutine%20immunisation%20of%20children%20has%20also%20almost%20stopped%20in%20the%20state%2C%20said%20Dr%20Shakeel%20Ur%20Rahman%2C%20one%20of%20the%20IDPD%20members%20who%20visited%20the%20state%20recently.%20The%20state%20government%20will%20need%20to%20launch%20catch-up%20campaigns%20for%20children%20who%20have%20missed%20out%20on%20immunisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20was%20also%20worried%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20being%20made%20available%20to%20the%20children%2C%20especially%2C%20in%20the%20camps%2C%20as%20the%20bulk%20of%20responsibility%20of%20running%20those%20camps%20is%20on%20the%20community%20or%20civil%20society%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20camp%20manager%20in%20a%20Meitei%20area%20told%20us%20that%20his%20team%20is%20able%20to%20give%20an%20egg%20once%20a%20week%20to%20the%20child.%20In%20a%20Kuki%20area%2C%20the%20team%20told%20us%20it%20is%20happening%20only%20once%20in%20fortnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20the%20situation%20returns%20to%20normalcy%2C%20then%20the%20government%20will%20have%20to%20give%20children%20Vitamin%20A%20orally%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20loss%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20said.%20Severe%20Vitamin%20A%20deficiency%20can%20cause%20eye%20damage%20and%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20dying%20from%20measles%20and%20diarrhoeal%20disease.%20Also%2C%20a%20measles%20immunisation%20drive%20is%20urgently%20needed%20for%20children%20in%20camps%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%2C%20leafy%20vegetables%20have%20also%20almost%20gone%20missing%20for%20four%20months%20now%2C%20the%20IDPD%20team%20found.%20And%20this%20could%20directly%20impact%20some%20of%20the%20health%20indicators%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20children.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5Report_MN.shtml%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS)-5%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20many%20as%2043%25%20children%20aged%20between%206-59%20months%20are%20already%20suffering%20from%20anaemia%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20overall%20anaemia%20in%20children%20went%20up%20to%2043%25%20in%202019-21%20(NFHS-5%20period)%20from%2023%25%20in%202015-16%20(NFHS-4%20period).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NFHS-5%20had%20already%20flagged%20the%20problem%20of%20undernutrition%20in%20the%20state.%20And%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%2C%20which%20have%20forced%20people%20to%20live%20in%20camps%20and%20have%20led%20to%20halting%20of%20various%20government%20programmes%20for%20children%2C%20might%20only%20end%20up%20increasing%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deficiency%20of%20various%20micronutrients%20are%20responsible%20for%20aggravating%20childhood%20morbidity%20and%20mortality.%20According%20to%20the%20NFHS-5%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20children%20who%20are%20stunted%20in%20the%20state%20decreased%20slightly%20from%2029%25%20to%2023%25%20in%20the%204%20years%20between%20NFHS-4%20and%20NFHS-5.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20continuing%20high%20levels%20of%20undernutrition%20are%20still%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20NFHS-5%20had%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22115809%2FScreenshot-2023-06-22-at-11.53.3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22115809%2FScreenshot-2023-06-22-at-11.53.3.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22115809%2FScreenshot-2023-06-22-at-11.53.3-300x155.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22115809%2FScreenshot-2023-06-22-at-11.53.3-1024x530.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22621%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20A%20camp%20housing%20those%20displaced%20by%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20in%20Imphal%20East%20camp.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20Humanitarian%20Commissioner%20for%20Relief%20(UNHCR)%20has%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20called%20%E2%80%98Sphere%20standards%E2%80%99%20for%20people%20living%20in%20relief%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CEither%20most%20of%20these%20guidelines%20were%20not%20being%20followed%20or%20only%20done%20so%20partially%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rahman%20observed%20about%20the%20camps%20the%20IDPD%20visited.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unhcr.org%2Fmedia%2Fsphere-project-humanitarian-charter-and-minimum-standards-humanitarian-response-2011-edition%5C%22%3ESphere%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%20pertain%20to%20minimum%20services%20that%20the%20people%20living%20in%20camps%20must%20get%20in%20four%C2%A0%20areas%3A%20water%20supply%2C%20sanitation%20and%20hygiene%3B%20food%20security%20and%20nutrition%3B%20shelter%20and%20settlement%3B%20and%20general%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmediate%20problems%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20long-term%20problems%20could%20potentially%20impact%20the%20people%2C%20especially%20children%2C%20living%20in%20the%20camps%2C%20the%20IDPD%20doctors%20also%20alluded%20to%20the%20immediate%20health%20problems%20that%20the%20four-month-long%20shutdown%20in%20the%20state%20has%20led%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20delivery%20services%20have%20near%20paralysed%20in%20the%20peripheral%20areas.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-healthcare-education-government-reel-under-violence%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%20earlier%2C%20the%20split%20along%20the%20community%20lines%20%E2%80%93%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20%E2%80%93%20among%20doctors%20and%20other%20healthcare%20providers%2C%20just%20like%20other%20professionals%2C%20is%20nearly%20complete.%20This%20ensured%20that%20doctors%20belonging%20to%20a%20particular%20community%20would%20not%20go%20to%20their%20healthcare%20facilities%20if%20they%20fell%20in%20the%20areas%20that%20were%20dominated%20by%20the%20other%20community%2C%20and%20vice-versa.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDPD%20doctors%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20even%20if%20security%20is%20promised%20to%20healthcare%20workers%20along%20the%20routes%20of%20their%20travel%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20agree%20to%20go%20for%20two%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20doctors%20of%20one%20community%20now%20can%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20work%20with%20their%20colleagues%20from%20the%20other%20community%3B%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20trust%20security%20forces%20because%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20their%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20doctors%20has%20led%20to%20inordinate%20delays%20in%20conducting%20many%20elective%20but%20necessary%20surgeries%20across%20the%20state%2C%20among%20many%20other%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSurgery%20is%20teamwork.%20If%20there%20is%20one%20member%20of%20the%20team%20present%2C%20s%2Fhe%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20anything%20if%20others%20are%20not%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Nara%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%2C%20if%20the%20team%20comprises%20doctors%20belonging%20to%20both%20the%20communities%2C%20then%20it%20is%20impossible%20that%20the%20full%20team%20would%20be%20at%20work%20on%20any%20given%20day%20%5Bin%20the%20current%20circumstances%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20four%20medical%20college-hospitals.%20Out%20of%20them%2C%20three%20are%20located%20in%20Imphal.%20The%20hills%2C%20where%20the%20Kuki%20population%20lives%2C%20has%20only%20one%20medical%20college-hospital%20which%20is%20in%20Churachandpur.%20This%20district%20got%20the%20medical%20college%20recently%20as%20its%20district%20hospital%20was%20converted%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20last%20edition%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.mohfw.gov.in%2Fnewshighlights-90%5C%22%3ERural%20Health%20Statistics%20(RHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20is%20a%20major%20scarcity%20of%20specialist%20doctors%20%E2%80%93%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%2C%20surgeons%2C%20paediatricians%20and%20physicians%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20community%20health%20centres%20(CHCs)%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20state%20has%2017%20CHCs.%20According%20to%20the%20RHS%2C%20against%20the%20requirement%20of%2017%20doctors%20specialising%20in%20%3Cem%3Eeach%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20various%20disciplines%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20are%20available%20at%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20CHCs%3A%20surgery%20(2)%2C%20Oostetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20(8)%2C%20physicians%20(2)%2C%20paediatricians%20(3)%20and%20eye%20surgeon%20(1).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shortage%20reveals%20how%20heavily%20the%20people%20living%20in%20peripheral%20areas%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20tertiary%20care%20centres%20of%20Imphal.%20As%20such%2C%20most%20people%20from%20the%20hills%20would%20rush%20to%20Imphal%20should%20specialist%20care%20be%20needed%20in%20the%20period%20when%20things%20were%20functioning%20normally%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20because%20of%20the%20ongoing%20violence%2C%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20living%20in%20the%20hills%20to%20the%20valley%20is%20completely%20restricted%2C%20thus%20bringing%20the%20referral%20to%20higher%20centres%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%20Therefore%2C%20now%20people%20are%20either%20travelling%20more%20than%20100%20km%20to%20reach%20Dimapur%20in%20Nagaland%20or%20Aizawl%20in%20Mizoram%20from%20the%20respective%20borders%20of%20the%20state.%20While%20a%20person%20with%20resources%20might%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20this%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20came%20across%20a%20patient%20in%20a%20Kangpopki%20camp%20who%20was%20suffering%20from%20scrub%20typhus%2C%20an%20infectious%20disease.%20For%20diagnosis%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Kohima%20but%20it%20was%20impossible%20for%20him%20to%20go%20there%20again%2C%20for%20a%20follow-up.%20And%20he%20was%20living%20in%20the%20camp%2C%20without%20access%20to%20any%20treatment%20as%20such.%20He%20was%20reported%20as%20having%20breathing%20issues%20among%20other%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20also%20found%20cases%20where%20patients%20who%20require%20routine%20dialysis%20were%20not%20able%20to%20get%20it%20done%20%E2%80%93%20which%20would%20worsen%20kidney%20disease.%20The%20IDPD%20team%2C%20which%20met%20two%20state%20government%20officials%2C%20recommended%20starting%20at%20least%20peritoneal%20dialysis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20less%20sophisticated%20process%20than%20hemodialysis%20which%20is%20usually%20preferred%20%E2%80%93%20but%20considering%20the%20current%20scenario%2C%20even%20the%20former%20would%20come%20handy.%20peritoneal%20dialysis%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Kangpopki%20primary%20health%20centre%2C%20where%20the%20team%20visited%2C%20it%20found%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20blood%20storage%20unit%2C%20forget%20a%20blood%20bank.%20So%20if%20a%20C-section%20patient%20required%20blood%20post%20the%20procedure%2C%20she%20would%20have%20no%20option%20because%20the%20route%20to%20Imphal%20was%20shut%20and%20there%20was%20no%20facility%20to%20get%20blood%20locally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20telemedicine%2C%20a%20service%20which%20receives%20special%20attention%20from%20policymakers%2C%20had%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20non-existent%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20internet%20ban.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20patients%20are%20not%20able%20to%20go%20physically%20and%20consult%20specialists%20in%20Imphal%2C%20telemedicine%20at%20least%20would%20have%20provided%20them%20some%20sort%20of%20an%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rahman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMaking%20prefabricated%20operation%20theatres%20and%20arranging%20mobile%20health%20facilities%20is%2C%20we%20hear%2C%20on%20the%20cards.%20But%20it%20defies%20common%20sense%20why%20it%20took%20so%20long%20for%20the%20government%20to%20think%20about%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Manglem%20Singh%20said.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20could%20have%20easily%20deputed%20doctors%20from%20outside%20the%20state%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20as%20they%20would%20not%20have%20a%20Meitei%20or%20a%20Kuki%20affiliation%2C%20and%20would%20have%20been%20easily%20worked%20in%20hospitals%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20doctors%20that%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20said%20a%20lot%20needed%20to%20be%20done%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20supply%20of%20medicines%20to%20people%20living%20in%20relief%20camps.%20The%20ones%20who%20suffer%20from%20diseases%20like%20hypertension%2C%20diabetes%20and%20cardiac%20problems%20need%20a%20constant%20flow%20of%20drugs%20which%20have%20turned%20elusive%20from%20them.%20This%20could%20lead%20to%20worsening%20of%20diseases%2C%20or%20even%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20senior%20official%20of%20the%20state%20government%20told%20us%20that%20there%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20medicine%20%3Cem%3Eper%20se%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20the%20distribution%20chain%2C%20which%20got%20broken%20due%20to%20the%20blockades%20and%20violence%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20an%20artificial%20shortage%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rahman%20said.%20For%20four%20months%20now%2C%20somehow%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20ensure%20through%20dialogue%20or%20whatever%20means%2C%20that%20the%20ones%20creating%20blockades%20should%20at%20least%20allow%20the%20movement%20of%20drugs%20and%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20RHS%2C%20the%20state%20has%20416%20health%20subcentres%2C%2086%20primary%20health%20centres%2C%2017%20community%20health%20centres%2C%20six%20district%20hospitals%20and%20three%20(now%20four)%20medical%20colleges-hospitals.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fhealth%2Fdeath-toll-mounts-as-manipur-conflict-stretches-healthcare-to-breaking-point-875261%5C%22%3EReports%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20from%20right%20from%20subcentres%20to%20medical%20colleges%2C%20all%20health%20facilities%20are%20grappling%20with%20medicines%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693969675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12082107%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.18.56.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmanipur-epidemics-may-break-out-in-relief-camps-if-urgent-measures-not-taken-warn-doctors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Routine%20immunisation%20for%20children%20has%20stopped%2C%20surgeries%20and%20dialysis%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20referral%20to%20higher%20health%20facilities%20has%20become%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20Shortage%20of%20medicines%20and%20restrictions%20on%20doctors'%20movements%20paralyse%20healthcare%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmanipur-epidemics-may-break-out-in-relief-camps-if-urgent-measures-not-taken-warn-doctors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Claude%20the%20koala%20unmasked%20as%20prolific%20plant%20thief%20in%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693969658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB52B%2Fproduction%2F_130997364_claude.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66713980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20ate%20thousands%20of%20seedlings%20that%20had%20been%20earmarked%20to%20help%20boost%20Australi