ure%20of%20the%20Indonesia%20visit%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%E2%80%99%20Secretary%20(East)%20Saurabh%20Kumar%20said%20that%20Modi%20will%20have%20no%20bilateral%20meetings%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20issue%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20new%20political%20map%20would%20be%20discussed%20at%20Jakarta%2C%20the%20senior%20diplomat%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20anticipate%20what%20would%20be%20discussed%20when%20the%20leaders%20meet%2C%20but%20issues%20which%20are%20of%20mutual%20concern%2C%20regional%20and%20international%2C%20would%20all%20come%20up%20once%20they%20have%20their%20discussion.%20Whether%20there%20would%20be%20a%20consensus%20or%20not%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20anticipate%20what%20would%20come%20out%20of%20the%20discussions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20lodged%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20protest%E2%80%9D%20with%20China%20over%20the%202023%20version%20of%20its%20standard%20map%20as%20it%20continued%20to%20show%20Aksai%20Chin%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20South%20East%20Asian%20regional%20association%20met%20in%20Jakarta%20on%20Tuesday%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20anxieties%20of%20the%20burgeoning%20China-US%20rivalry%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20earlier%20differences%20on%20its%20approach%20towards%20Myanmar%2C%20ASEAN%20upheld%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20invite%20the%20junta%20government%20to%20regional%20meetings.%20Further%2C%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20chance%20to%20chair%20the%20bloc%20in%202026%20has%20now%20been%20given%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2F5%2Fmyanmar-will-not-be-allowed-asean-leadership-in-2026%5C%22%3EASEAN%20agreed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20five-point%20peace%20consensus%20plan%20would%20continue%20to%20guide%20its%20approach%20