20West%2C%20strategists%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitch's%20recent%20downgrade%20of%20the%20US%20credit%20rating%20to%20AA%20from%20AAA%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20low%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20risk%20is%20magnified%20by%20environmental%20'arbitrage'%2C%20where%20carbon%20intensive%20industries%20such%20as%20manufacturing%2C%20commodity%20production%2C%20etc.%2C%20were%20outsourced%20to%20the%20East%2C%20leaving%20the%20West%20industrially%20fragile%20and%20susceptible%20to%20inflation%20shocks%2C%26quot%3B%20JPMorgan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20West's%20inability%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20produce%20sufficient%20supplies%20of%20natural%20gas%2C%20cheap%20food%2C%20or%20munitions%20for%20Ukraine%20are%20some%20examples%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20note%20from%20Thursday%2C%20JPMorgan%20analysts%20pointed%20out%20signs%20of%20de-dollarization%20already%20taking%20root.%20Looking%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdedollarization-us-dollar-greenback-losing-influence-oil-markets-jpmorgan-yuan-2023-9%5C%22%3Eoil%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20commodity%20is%20increasingly%20being%20transacted%20in%20non-dollar%20currencies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20yuan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBu%20while%20JPMorgan%20expects%20%26quot%3Bmarginal%20de-dollarization%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20place%2C%20the%20pace%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20be%20rapid.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20dollar%20is%20just%20too%20widely%20used%20in%20a%20vast%20global%20financial%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20partial%20de-dollarization%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%20the%20renminbi%20assumes%20some%20of%20the%20current%20functions%20of%20the%20dollar%20among%20non-aligned%20countries%20and%20China's%20trading%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20is%20more%20plausible%2C%20especially%20against%20a%20backdro