est%20in%20the%20evening%20of%20the%20same%20day%2C%20which%20came%20out%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20president%20will%20test%20at%20a%20regular%20cadence%20this%20week%20and%20monitor%20for%20symptoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2023%2F09%2F04%2Fstatement-from-white-house-press-secretary-karine-jean-pierre-3%2F%5C%22%3EKarine%20Jean-Pierre%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20test%20on%20Tuesday%20also%20came%20out%20negative%20for%20Biden.%20As%20per%20the%20White%20House%2C%20he%20will%20wear%20masks%20indoors%20due%20to%20his%20exposure%20to%20the%20first%20lady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Flady-jill-biden-tests-positive-covid-19%2Fstory%3Fid%3D102918037%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20lady%20was%20last%20with%20President%20Biden%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20same%20day%20that%20she%20tested%20positive%20for%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20isolating%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Rehoboth%20Beach%2C%20Delaware%2C%20and%20Biden%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20public%20health%20authorities%20had%20observed%20an%20uptick%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F28%2Fus%2Fcovid-cases-hospitalizations.html%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20number%20of%20COVID-19%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2F4%2Fwhat-is-pirola-the-newest-ba-2-86-coronavirus-variant-that-is-spreading%5C%22%3Etwo%20new%20variants%20raising%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20is%20scheduled%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20G20%20summit%20taking%20place%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%209-10