0ultimately%20a%20negative%20for%20asset%20prices%20and%20the%20broader%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20both%20premises%20for%20our%20cautious%20outlook%20(rates%20and%20geopolitics)%20turned%20more%20negative%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20while%20positioning%20and%20valuations%20increased%2C%20we%20think%20there%20is%20now%20a%20higher%20likelihood%20of%20a%20crisis%20over%20the%20next%20six%20to%2012%20months%2C%20the%20severity%20of%20which%20could%20be%20higher%20than%20market%20participants%20anticipate%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolanovic%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETighter%20monetary%20policy%20from%20the%20Fed%20is%20negatively%20impacting%20consumer%20credit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-debt-recession-warning-us-economy-outlook-wells-fargo-2023-8%5C%22%3Ewith%20delinquency%20rates%20on%20the%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20commercial%20real%20estate%20has%20been%20hit%20hard%20by%20work-from-home%20trends%20just%20before%20the%20sector%20will%20have%20to%20refinance%20debt%20at%20much%20higher%20borrowing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-looming-companies-debt-refinancing-costs-rise-fidelity-economist-2023-9%5C%22%3Eknock-on%20effects%20from%20higher%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20market%20volatility%20and%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20employment%2C%20according%20to%20Kolanovic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20AI-fueled%20rally%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%20isn't%20helping%20the%20situation%2C%20as%20it%20will%20likely%20prove%20to%20be%20fleeting%20for%20investors.%20He%20said%20expectations%20that%20AI%20will%20transform%20the%20US%20economy%20in%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%20are%20%26quot%3Bunrealistic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kolanovic%20to%20turn%20more%20bullish%20on%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20see%20two%20things%20%E2%80%94%20and