%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20higher%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20leading%20to%20lower%20demand%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20according%20to%20home%20builders%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20ultimately%20translates%20into%20lower%20demand%20for%20lumber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20interest%20rates%20get%20to%206.5%25%20the%20waters%20will%20get%20very%20choppy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Tampa%20home%20builder%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realestateconsulting.com%2F%5C%22%3EJohn%20Burns%20Real%20Estate%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRickPalaciosJr%2Fstatus%2F1567855122310656000%5C%22%3Ein%20its%20August%20survey.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Another%20builder%20in%20Harrisburg%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20big%20uptick%20in%20buying%20activity%20when%20mortgage%20rates%20briefly%20dipped%20in%20early%20August%20to%205%25%2C%20signaling%20how%20strongly%20correlated%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20to%20home%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAugust%20was%20a%20very%20poor%20month%20for%20sales%20across%20the%20board.%20Cancellations%20spiked%20from%20July%20and%20buyers%20showed%20no%20sense%20of%20urgency%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Austin%20home%20builder%20told%20John%20Burns%20Real%20Estate%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20could%20continue%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20lumber%20market%2C%20if%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20moves%20forward%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Faugust-goldilocks-jobs-report-confirms-75-basis-point-fed-hike-2022-9%5C%22%3Ea%20widely%20expected%2075%20basis%20point%20interest%20rate%20hikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20FOMC%20meeting%20later%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20little%20lag%20between%20mortgage%20rates%20and%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20Federal%20Funds%20Rate%2C%20as%20has%20been%20seen%20when%20the%20Fed%20first%20began%20raising%20rates%20in%20March%2C%20precisely%20when%20mortgage%20rates%20also%20began%20to%20soar.%20But%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-september-rally-likely-cooling-inflation-data-seasonals-2022-9%5C%22%3Einflation%20continues%20to%20cool%20down%20as%20some%20Wall%20Street%20strategists%20expect%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Fed%20pivot%20may%20be%20right%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20limiting%20further%20rate%20hikes%20and%20therefore%20capping%20the%20rise%20in%20mortgage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20resurgence%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20thus%20aiding%20the%20price%20of%20lumber.%20If%20not%2C%20lumber%20prices%20could%20return%20to%20its%20pre-pandemic%20trading%20range%20of%20between%20%24200%20and%20%24600%20per%20thousand%20board%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20upshot%20of%20a%20slowing%20housing%20market%20is%20that%20input%20supplies%2C%20including%20lumber%2C%20are%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20demand%20as%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20begin%20to%20work%20themselves%20out.%20%26quot%3BA%20slowdown%20in%20sales%20helped%20to%20relieve%20the%20pressure%20on%20labor%20and%20supply%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Philadelphia%20home%20builder%20told%20John%20Burns%20Real%20Estate%20Consulting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flumber-prices-defy-housing-mortgage-rate-surge-to-six-percent-2022-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693941642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631b8138c3104e00125056e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Flumber-prices-defy-housing-mortgage-rate-surge-to-six-percent-2022-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20interest%20rates%20get%20to%206.5%25%20the%20waters%20will%20get%20very%20choppy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Tampa%20home%20builder%20told%20John%20Burns%20Real%20Estate%20Consulting%C2