%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpnb-introduces-cbdc-upi-interoperability-for-seamless-transactions-123090501224_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpnb-introduces-cbdc-upi-interoperability-for-seamless-transactions-123090501224_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%20After%20Confirming%20Xi's%20Absence%20From%20G20%2C%20China%20Claims%20Relations%20With%20India%20Are%20%E2%80%98Stable%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31211511%2FW020230531715249452708final.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20it%20officially%20announced%20that%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fxi-jinping-li-qiang-g20-india-china%5C%22%3Ewill%20not%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China%20said%20that%20relations%20with%20India%20%E2%80%9Cremain%20stable%20on%20the%20whole%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20Beijing%20was%20willing%20to%20work%20%E2%80%9Cto%20promote%20greater%20development%20of%20China-India%20relations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20days%20of%20buzz%20about%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20attendance%2C%20China%20officially%20confirmed%20on%20Monday%20(September%204)%20that%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20represent%20the%20country%20at%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20official%20reason%20given%20for%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20absence%2C%20who%20had%20just%20recently%20visited%20South%20Africa%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Xi%20will%20be%20skipping%20a%20G20%20summit%20since%202013%2C%20barring%20his%20absence%20in%202021%E2%80%99s%20Rome%20summit%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20restrictions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20not%20officially%20responded%20about%20the%20Chinese%20president%20not%20travelling%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20summit%2C%20which%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20showcased%20as%20a%20major%20foreign%20policy%20achievement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Tuesday%20(September%205)%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20was%20asked%20whether%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20stay%20away%20reflected%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1698976403507888392%5C%22%3Easserted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China%20has%20%E2%80%9Calways%20attached%20great%20importance%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20G20%20and%20supported%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20in%20hosting%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20summit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20all%20parties%20to%20push%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20Asian%20giants%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1698976603802615851%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENing%20asserted%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cbilateral%20relations%20remain%20stable%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20with%20dialogue%20and%20communication%20at%20all%20levels%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwatch-xis-refusal-to-attend-g20-marks-further-deterioration-in-relations-modi-must-be-more-transparent%5C%22%3EXi%E2%80%99s%20Refusal%20to%20Attend%20G20%20Marks%20Further%20Deterioration%20in%20Relations%2C%20Modi%20Must%20Be%20More%20Transparent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Beijing%20believes%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20improvement%20and%20development%20of%20China-India%20relations%20is%20in%20the%20common%20interest%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20the%20two%20peoples%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20India%20to%20promote%20greater%20development%20of%20China-India%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20Mao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20China%20have%20largely%20remained%20frozen%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20border%20stand-off%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20clash%20that%20killed%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20four%20Chinese%20soldiers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20leading%20to%20disengagement%20in%20around%20four%20to%20five%20points.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fexplained-what-are-the-friction-points-on-the-lac%2Farticle66928561.ece%5C%22%3Etwo%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20which%20both%20sides%20remain%20eyeball-to-eyeball%20in%20the%20high%20Himalayas%20at%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20not%20held%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20since%202019.%20There%20have%20been%20ministerial%20meetings%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20various%20multilateral%20events%2C%20but%20India%20has%20indicated%20that%20they%20were%20limited%20to%20discussing%20the%20border%20stand-off.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20absence%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F09%2F04%2Fdel70-g20-jaishankar.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20on%20Monday%20night%20that%20the%20focus%20should%20not%20be%20on%20the%20level%20of%20representation%20of%20countries%2C%20but%20on%20their%20agendas%20for%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20countries%20are%20represented%20by%20whoever%20they%20have%20chosen%20to%20represent%20them.%20The%20levels%20of%20representation%20do%20not%20become%20the%20final%20determinant%20of%20the%20position%20of%20a%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20now%2C%20two%20heads%20of%20states%20have%20officially%20bowed%20out%20from%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20G20%20summit.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fvladimir-putin-will-not-attend-g20-summit-india%5C%22%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20he%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20he%20needs%20to%20concentrate%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20military%20operation%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20the%20Russian%20term%20for%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20announcement%2C%20the%20Mexican%20president%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20long%20foreign%20trips%20and%20has%20not%20attended%20any%20in-person%20G20%20summits%20since%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693928735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31211511%2FW020230531715249452708final.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-claims-relations-with-india-are-stable%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20not%20officially%20responded%20about%20the%20Chinese%20president%20not%20travelling%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20summit%2C%20which%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20showcased%20as%20a%20major%20foreign%20policy%20achievement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http