l-engineering-jv-bags-rs-1-275-crore-project-in-madhya-pradesh-123090501165_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Summit%202023%3A%20Will%20cars%20be%20allowed%20between%208-10%20September%202023%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693926143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103402990%2Cimgsize-101804.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fpolicy-and-industry%2Fg20-summit-2023-will-cars-be-allowed-between-8-10-september-2023%2Farticleshow%2F103399718.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Police%20clarified%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20miscommunication%20regarding%20the%20traffic%20restrictions%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%20They%20stated%20that%20the%20capital%20would%20not%20be%20closed%20during%20the%20event%20and%20that%20restrictions%20would%20only%20be%20applicable%20in%20small%20portions%20of%20the%20NDMC%20area%20for%20short%20intervals%20of%20time.%20Private%20vehicles%20and%20cabs%20will%20be%20allowed%20through%20the%20borders%2C%20but%20residents%20are%20encouraged%20to%20take%20the%20Metro%20route.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRACHI%20AHLUWALIA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fpolicy-and-industry%2Fg20-summit-2023-will-cars-be-allowed-between-8-10-september-2023%2Farticleshow%2F103399718.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20Moves%20Supreme%20Court%20Against%20Manipur%20Police's%20FIRs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F13173828%2FManipur_police.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20executive%20committee%20of%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%20(EGI)%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%20(September%205)%20condemning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-editors-guild-fact-finding-team-cites-revoked-sec-66a%5C%22%3EManipur%20police%E2%80%99s%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20against%20its%20members%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20day%20later%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20it%20has%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20police%20filed%20FIRs%20against%20the%20EGI%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20Seema%20Mustafa%2C%20as%20well%20as%20three%20other%20members%20%E2%80%93%20Seema%20Guha%2C%20Bharat%20Bhushan%20and%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%20%E2%80%93%20who%20constituted%20a%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20visited%20the%20state%20to%20study%20media%20reportage%20of%20its%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Guild%20is%20extremely%20disturbed%20that%20rather%20than%20respond%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20in%20the%20report%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20registered%20FIRs%20invoking%20multiple%20provisions%20of%20the%20%5BIndian%20Penal%20Code%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20EGI%E2%80%99s%20executive%20committee%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findeditorsguild%2Fstatus%2F1699032909745680404%5C%22%3Estatement%20posted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20shocked%20by%20the%20intimidatory%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%2C%20Mr%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20is%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20one%20Ngangom%20Sarat%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20worker%E2%80%9D%20who%20lives%20in%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20refers%20to%20a%20photo%20caption%20in%20the%20fact-finding%20team%E2%80%99s%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarat%20said%20the%20caption%20claimed%20that%20smoke%20was%20rising%20from%20a%20Kuki%20home%20when%20in%20fact%20it%20was%20the%20home%20of%20a%20forest%20official.%20Based%20on%20this%2C%20Sarat%20decided%20that%20the%20report%20was%20false%20in%20entirety%20and%20%E2%80%9Csponsored%20by%20Kuki%20militants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEGI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndEditorsGuild%2Fstatus%2F1698287099265561025%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3Eacknowledged%20the%20error%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20uploaded%20a%20corrected%20version%20of%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20(September%204)%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1698582733273088015%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DJ1VjQNDTFWrXclPML16-LA%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20because%20EGI%20staff%20were%20%E2%80%9Ctrying%20to%20create%20more%20clashes%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3Eviewed%20by%20many%20as%20acting%20in%20a%20partisan%20manner%3C%2Fa%3E%20favourable%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20and%20EGI%E2%80%99s%20fact-finding%20report%20reflects%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20clear%20indications%20that%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20state%20became%20partisan%20during%20the%20conflict.%20It%20should%20have%20avoided%20taking%20sides%20in%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20but%20it%20failed%20to%20do%20its%20duty%20as%20a%20democratic%20government%20which%20should%20have%20represented%20the%20entire%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20net%20result%20is%20that%20the%20executive%2C%20its%20instruments%20(the%20police%20and%20other%20security%20forces%20of%20the%20state)%20and%20the%20bureaucracy%20are%20today%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%20There%20is%20a%20Meitei%20government%2C%20Meitei%20police%20and%20Meitei%20bureaucracy%20in%20Imphal%20and%20the%20tribal%20people%20living%20in%20the%20hills%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20would%20say%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20partisan%20actions%20had%20in%20fact%20pushed%20the%20state%20into%20turmoil%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20found%20that%20the%20ban%20on%20internet%20services%20in%20the%20state%20drove%20the%20media%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20narrative%20under%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20dispensation%20became%20a%20narrow%20ethnic%20one%20playing%20up%20to%20the%20biases%20of%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEGI%E2%80%99s%20executive%20council%20pointed%20out%20in%20its%20statement%20that%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20its%20report%20contradicted%20India%E2%80%99s%20projection%20of%20itself%20as%20a%20leading%20democracy%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20close%20the%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6The%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20labelling%20of%20the%20journalists%E2%80%99%20body%20%5Bthe%20EGI%5D%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-state%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20way%20the%20Union%20Government%20has%20emphasised%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20credentials%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spirit%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20at%20the%20global%20stage%20for%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20statement%20has%20been%20reproduced%20in%20full%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPRESS%20STATEMENT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20Indis%20is%20disturbed%20by%20the%20registration%20of%20First%20Information%20Reports%20(FIRs)%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20against%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Guild%20as%20well%20as%20the%20members%20of%20the%20fact-%20finding%20team%20that%20had%20visited%20Manipur%20to%20study%20and%20document%20media%E2%80%99s%20coverage%20of%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Guild%20is%20further%20shocked%20by%20the%20intimidatory%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20Chief%20Muster%20of%20Manipur%2C%20Mr.%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guild%20had%20received%20several%20representations%20from%20civil%20society%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indian%20Army%20raising%20concerns%20that%20the%20media%20in%20Manipur%20was%20playing%20a%20partisan%20role%20in%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20between%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20Kuki-Chin%20minority.%20The%20Guild%20had%20sent%20a%20three-member%20team%20to%20Manipur%20to%20examine%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20reportage%20in%20the%20state%20as%20well%20as%20the%20effects%20of%20internet%20shut%20down.%20The%20team%20met%20a%20cross-section%20of%20reporters%2C%20editors%2C%20representatives%20of%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20Manipur%2C%20All%20Manipur%20Working%20Journalists%20Union%2C%20civil%20society%20activists%2C%20public%20intellectuals%2C%20women%20affected%20by%20the%20violence%2C%20tribal%20spokespersons%20and%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20security%20forces%20operating%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20released%20on%20September%202%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guild%20is%20extremely%20disturbed%20that%20rather%20than%20respond%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20in%20the%20report%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20registered%20FIRs%20invoking%20multiple%20provisions%20of%20the%20IPC.%20The%20Guild%20has%20already%20acknowledged%20and%20corrected%20an%20error%20that%20was%20pointed%20out%20regarding%20a%20photo%20caption%2C%20and%20we%20remain%20open%20to%20further%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20labelling%20of%20the%20journalists%20body%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-State%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20way%20the%20Union%20Government%20has%20emphasised%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20credentials%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spirit%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20at%20the%20global%20stage%20for%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guild%20would%20also%20like%20to%20reiterate%20that%20the%20underlying%20idea%20of%20the%20report%20was%20to%20enable%20introspection%20and%20reflection%20on%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%20such%20a%20sensitive%20situation.%20The%20Guild%20urges%20the%20state%20government%20to%20close%20the%20FIRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExecutive%20Committee%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEditors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20report%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20news%20of%20the%20Guild%20moving%20SC.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693925379000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F13173828%2FManipur_police.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fegi-condemns-manipur-police-fir-against-its-members%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20ago%2C%20the%20Guild%20had%20released%20a%20statement%20criticising%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh's%20move%20to%20term%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20released%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20indicting%20the%20state%20government's%20partisan%20role%20in%20the%20ethnic%C2%A0violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fegi-condemns-manipur-police-fir-against-its-members%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Started%20For%20My%20Daughter%E2%80%99%3A%20Assam%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Vermicompost%20Biz%20Earns%20Her%20Rs%203.5%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202008.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kanika%20Talukdar%20was%20abound%20with%20happiness%20as%20her%20daughter%20was%20born%20after%20three%20years%20of%20her%20marriage.%20But%20this%20happiness%20could%20not%20last%20long%20because%20soon%20after%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20down%20with%20a%20fever%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20We%20found%20out%20that%20he%20had%20malaria.%20The%20local%20doctor%20referred%20him%20to%20a%20Guwahati%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20Along%20with%20my%20father%2C%20he%20left%20for%20the%20city%20for%20his%20treatment%2C%20but%20soon%20we%20got%20the%20news%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Borjhar%20village%20resident%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20very%20small.%20While%20we%20were%20grieving%20the%20death%20of%20my%20husband%2C%20her%20entire%20future%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20was%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20My%20parents%20brought%20me%20back%20home%20from%20my%20in-laws%E2%80%99.%20I%20thought%20of%20working%20as%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20an%20unwanted%20%3Cem%3Ebojh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(burden)%20for%20my%20elderly%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20encouraged%20Kanika%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%20towards%20self-empowerment.%20Today%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20runs%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249941%2Fhow-to-vermicompost-earn-revenue-sana-khan-sj-organics-earthworms-uttar-pradesh-sustainability-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evermicompost%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20earns%20her%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20just%20Rs%20500%20of%20her%20savings%20and%201%20kg%20of%20earthworms%20provided%20by%20KVK%20in%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20she%20started%20the%20vermicompost%20business.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20just%20Rs%20500%20of%20her%20savings%20and%201%20kg%20of%20earthworms%20provided%20by%20KVK%20in%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20Kanika%20started%20the%20vermicompost%20business.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20She%20Started%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20till%20class%2012%2C%20Kanika%20struggled%20financially%20and%20professionally.%20To%20fend%20for%20herself%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20she%20worked%20low-paying%20jobs%20like%20weaving.%20For%20every%20Assamese%20saree%20she%20weaved%2C%20she%20would%20only%20get%20Rs%201%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20take%20at%20least%20eight%20days%20to%20weave%20a%20saree.%20I%20could%20barely%20earn%20Rs%204%2C000%20in%20a%20month.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20for%20us%20to%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%202014%20that%20she%20attended%20a%20workshop%20and%20came%20a