my%20daughter%20in%20a%20good%20school.%20I%20wish%20she%20either%20becomes%20a%20doctor%20or%20gets%20into%20an%20agriculture%20university.%20Previously%2C%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20comfortable%20asking%20my%20parents%20for%20money.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20ask%20for%20money%20from%20anyone%20today.%20With%20my%20earnings%2C%20I%20also%20got%20my%20home%20renovated%20and%20constructed%20an%20office%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Kanika%20was%20conferred%20the%20national-level%20Padma%20awards%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%20I%20could%20not%20have%20even%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20get%20recognition%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20happiness%20cannot%20be%20expressed%20in%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Kanika%20Talukdar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693920685000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kanika%20Talukdar's%20life%20was%20shattered%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20malaria.%20To%20overcome%20financial%20hardships%20and%20look%20after%20her%20four-month-old%20daughter%2C%20she%20started%20selling%20vermicompost.%20She%20shares%20how%20she%20started%20with%20just%20Rs%20500.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329041%2Fassam-woman-starts-vermicompost-business-after-husband-death-earns-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assessing%20Manipur's%20Healthcare%20Challenges%20Amidst%20the%20Ongoing%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12081122%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.08.47-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20part%20of%20a%20two-part%20explainer%20on%20the%20need%20to%20assess%20the%20healthcare%20costs%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Manipur%20conflict%20on%20its%20state-population.%20T%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnesinfosphere.com%2Four-work%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInfoSphere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20team%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20its%20field%20team%2C%20has%20written%20this%20piece.%20The%20piece%20also%20says%20that%20a%20paucity%20of%20local%20data%20remains%20a%20challenge.%20The%20conflict%20situations%20exacerbate%20these%20challenges%2C%20making%20any%20data%20analytical%20exercise%20a%20difficult%20process.%20You%20can%20access%20the%20InfoSphere%20edition%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnesinfosphere.com%2F_files%2Fugd%2F85c814_66f6d1d42239442dacf25afb9974e058.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20occupies%2022%2C327%20square%20kilometres%20of%20area%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%2028%2C55%2C794%20people%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censusindia2011.com%2Fmanipur-population.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DManipur%2520Population%2520%252D%2520Census%2520India%25202011%26amp%3Btext%3DAs%2520per%2520the%2520Census%2520India%2Cis%252013.14%2525%2520of%2520total%2520population.%5C%22%3E2011%20Census.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20Regional%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20a%20state%20hospital%2C%20seven%20district%20hospitals%2C%20one%20sub-district%20hospital%2C%2016%20community%20health%20centres%2C%2080%20primary%20health%20centres%2C%20413%20sub-centres%20and%2033%20private%20hospitals%2Fclinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20also%20has%20a%20fairly%20decent%20sex%20ratio%20of%20987%20girls%20born%20for%20every%201%2C000%20boys.%20The%20ratio%20declines%20to%20957%20girls%20for%20every%201%2C000%20boys%20for%20ages%20below%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202023-24%20budget%2C%20the%20state%20increased%20its%20allocation%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fstates%2Fmanipur-budget-analysis-2023-24%5C%22%3E10%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20to%20ramp%20up%20health%20facilities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20understand%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20culture%20and%20history%20to%20get%20a%20complete%20picture%20of%20their%20healthcare%20system%20and%20the%20various%20stakeholders%20involved%20in%20its%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvolution%20of%20healthcare%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20A%20comparison%20between%20NFHS-4%20and%20NFHS-5%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20has%20gone%20through%20several%20phases%20of%20development.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20healthcare%20was%20primarily%20limited%20to%20traditional%20practices%20and%20local%20remedies.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20modern%20medicine%2C%20the%20state%20saw%20the%20establishment%20of%20government-run%20healthcare%20centres%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20immunisation%20programmes%20and%20family%20planning%20initiatives%20further%20enhanced%20healthcare%20services%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Manipur%20still%20faces%20plenty%20of%20healthcare%20issues%20which%20add%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20its%20residents.%20The%20poor%20condition%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20affects%20some%20communities%20more%20than%20the%20others.%20These%20include%20women%2C%20children%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20and%20people%20with%20different%20ailments.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20paramount%20to%20look%20at%20the%20statistics%20when%20analysing%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20in%20any%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20expenditure%20on%20healthcare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS)-4%2C%202015-16%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20per%20capita%20public%20health%20expenditure%20stands%20at%20Rs%201%2C364.%20This%20is%20almost%20three%20times%20that%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20double%20the%20expenditure%20of%20Punjab%20and%20the%20national%20average%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20such%20a%20high%20expenditure%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20households%20with%20any%20usual%20member%20covered%20by%20a%20health%20scheme%20or%20health%20insurance%20is%20only%203.6%25%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20lower%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2028.7%25.%20The%20coverage%20is%20even%20more%20limited%20in%20the%20hilly%20districts%2C%20with%20Senapati%2C%20Ukhrul%2C%20and%20Chandel%20having%20coverage%20rates%20of%20only%200.6%25%2C%201%25%2C%20and%201.1%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20indicates%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20population%20pays%20for%20medical%20expenses%20out%20of%20their%20own%20pockets%2C%20leading%20to%20financial%20burden%20and%20challenges%20in%20accessing%20quality%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279.png%20910w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05172527%2Fimage-1279-300x139.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-ima