hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fhiv-prevalence-rate-among-adults-highest-in-manipur-study%2Fstory-8qpmdnceFybIqJxXTr5Z5N.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20the%20highest%20prevalence%20of%20HIV%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20adult%20population%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%20rate%20of%201.15%25.%20This%20is%20four%20times%20the%20all-India%20average%20and%20indicates%20a%20significant%20public%20health%20challenge%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20over%20half%20of%20the%20deliveries%20in%20private%20health%20facilities%20in%20urban%20Manipur%20are%20performed%20by%20a%20caesarean%20section%2C%20while%20the%20percentage%20is%20lower%20(30%25)%20in%20public%20health%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-healthcare-education-government-reel-under-violence%5C%22%3EMedicine%20Shortages%2C%20Uncertain%20Educational%20Futures%3A%20Manipur%20Is%20Reeling%20Under%20Many%20Impacts%20of%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20manpower%20and%20infrastructure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NFHS-4%20and%20District%20Level%20Household%20and%20Facility%20Survey%204%2C%20Manipur%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20nurses%20per%20capita%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20after%20Kerala.%20This%20indicates%20a%20relatively%20better%20availability%20of%20nursing%20staff%20for%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05174321%2Fimage-1283.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05174321%2Fimage-1