0one%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births).%20In%20NFHS-4%2C%20IMR%20was%2021.7.%20The%20under-five%20mortality%20rate%20during%20the%20period%20remained%20nearly%20the%20same%20at%20around%2030%2C%20(meaning%2030%20deaths%20before%20the%20age%20of%20five%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20teams%20have%20been%20constituted%20in%20each%20of%20the%20affected%20districts%20in%20Manipur%20to%20provide%20overall%20healthcare%20services%20to%20the%20victims%20at%20the%20designated%20relief%20camps.%20Regular%20health%20check-ups%20are%20conducted%20at%20all%20the%20designated%20relief%20camps%20across%20the%20state%2C%20and%20those%20who%20are%20seriously%20ill%20are%20promptly%20transferred%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospitals%20by%20ambulance%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20healthcare%20services%20for%20women%20and%20children%2C%20including%20lactating%20mothers%20and%20infants%2C%20are%20provided%20under%20the%20maternal%20health%20and%20child%20health%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22954%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284.png%20954w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05175720%2Fimage-1284-300x193.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671573%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%2068.8%25%20of%20children%20in%20Manipur%2C%20aged%2012-23%20months%2C%20received%20all%20basic%20vaccinations%20against%20tuberculosis%2C%20diphtheria%2C%20pertussis%2C%20tetanus%2C%20polio%2C%20and%20measles.%20Only%20around%202.8%25%20of%20children%20(aged%2012-23%20months)%20in%20the%20state%20had%20not%20received%20any%20vaccinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2042%25%20of%20children%20(aged%20between%20six%20and%2059%20months)%20in%20the%20state%20suffered%20from%20anaemia%20%E2%80%93%20a%20substantial%20increase%20from%20the%20NFHS-4%20estimate%20of%2022.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%2063.8%25%20of%20women%20used%20cloth%2C%2080.9%25%20used%20sanitary%20napkins%2C%203.9%25%20used%20locally%20prepared%20napkins%2C%200.7%25%20used%20menstrual%20cups%20and%200.1%25%20used%20tampons.%20Thirty-seven%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20(aged%20between%2018%20to%2049%20years)%20in%20the%20state%20reported%20having%20experienced%20either%20physical%20or%20sexual%20violence%20and%204%25%20reported%20having%20experienced%20both.%20However%2C%20only%203%25%20of%20women%20who%20had%20experienced%20such%20violence%20sought%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20put%20some%20of%20these%20numbers%20in%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20insight%20from%20the%20NFHS%20surveys%20and%20other%20sources%20may%20help%20provide%20greater%20depth%20to%20our%20team%E2%80%99s%20analysis%2C%20however%2C%20access%20to%20these%20figures%20and%20granular%20details%20remains%20a%20challenge.%20Our%20team%20also%20faced%20these%20challenges.%20If%20we%20could%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20through%20better%20(high%20frequency)%20data%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20helpful%20for%20both%20context%20and%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssessing%20the%20socio-political%20and%20economic%20situation%20in%20a%20conflict-affected%20area%20leads%20to%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20demographic%E2%80%99s%20public%20health%20scenario%2C%20too.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20too%2C%20many%20issues%20highlighted%20in%20this%20piece%20have%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20elderly%2C%20who%20have%20all%20been%20badly%20affected%20by%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20this%20series%20shall%20reflect%20more%20on%20the%20role%20of%20other%20factors%20responsible%20for%20the%20healthcare%20implications%20of%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eis%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAmisha%20Singh%2C%20Aditi%20Desai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shalaka%20Adhikari%2C%20Samragnee%20Chakraborty%2C%20Shilpa%20Santhosh%20and%20Vasudevan%20%3Cem%3Eare%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES%20and%20members%20of%20the%20InfoSphere%20Team.%20The%20authors%20thank%20Dr%20Samrat%20Sinha%20for%20his%20constant%20guidance%2C%20help%20and%20support.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20previous%20field%20studies%20from%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20Manipur%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fauthor%2F1779734%2Fsamrat-sinha%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frelief-manipur-trucks%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-multi-faceted-economic-ramifications-of-manipurs-ethnic-conflict%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-sexual-violence-bjp-apathy-patriarchy%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693920656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12081122%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.08.47-1.png%22%2C%22origin