the%20loopholes%20in%20the%20medical%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20country%20through%20the%20story%20of%2019-year-old%20Poonam%20Gond.%20The%20Chhatisgarh%20native%20battles%20sickle%20cell%20disease%20%E2%80%94%20a%20genetic%20blood%20disorder%20that%20necessitates%20frequent%20blood%20transfusions.%20But%20as%20the%20report%20cited%2C%20%E2%80%9Cone%20doctor%20for%20every%2016%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D%20meant%20Gond%20was%20not%20on%20the%20priority%20list.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20list%20was%20endless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20instances%20underline%20the%20domino%20effect%20that%20understaffed%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326524%2Ffood-for-patiets-of-diabetes-cancer-pcos-home-delivery-hypothalamus-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder-resourced%20rural%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20have%20on%20patient%20care.%20But%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccitizen-led%20initiative%E2%80%9D%20spearheaded%20by%20three%20friends%20is%20attempting%20to%20change%20this%20grim%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20nation%2C%20Mission%20ICU%20was%20conceived%20by%20Dr%20Ashwin%20Naik%2C%20Maanoj%20Shah%2C%20and%20Dr%20Edmond%20Fernandes.%20As%20they%20share%20their%20journey%20and%20plans%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20one%20can%20agree%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%20is%20changing%20as%20we%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20disparity%20brought%20about%20by%20COVID%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201033px)%20100vw%2C%201033px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221033%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20ICU%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%2020%20hospitals%20across%20India%20including%20in%20districts%20of%20