%20Mission%20ICU%20to%20be%20integrated.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20he%20informs%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20scanned%20around%20100%20hospitals%20to%20finalise%2010%20that%20really%20needed%20this%20facility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201027px)%20100vw%2C%201027px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221027%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20ICU%20aims%20to%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20that%20rural%20patients%20take%20to%20reach%20the%20ICU%20to%2030%20minutes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302.jpg%201027w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302-300x253.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302-500x421.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302-768x647.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-2-1-1693911302-150x126.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329084%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMission%20ICU%20aims%20to%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20that%20rural%20patients%20take%20to%20reach%20the%20ICU%20to%2030%20minutes%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Maanoj%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Health%20Index%20(BHI)%202023%E2%80%99%20surveyed%20over%2010%2C000%20retailers%20across%20rural%20India%20for%20over%20a%20month.%20The%20conclusion%20was%20that%20only%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20semi-rural%20and%20rural%20population%20in%20India%20have%20access%20to%20modern%20healthcare%20within%20their%20localities.%20The%20survey%20also%20reported%20that%2090%2