%2Fnovo-nordisk-lvmh-europe-valuable-company_n_64f24514e4b0ca54cc6c2dae%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Turns%20Grandpa%E2%80%99s%20Old%20Shop%20into%20Multi-Crore%20Biz%2C%20Revives%20Wood%20Cold-Pressed%20Oils%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20childhood%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Sibi%20Manivannan%20would%20relish%20the%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20mother%20cooked%2C%20and%20even%20today%2C%20at%2030%2C%20remembers%20the%20exact%20aroma%20and%20taste%20of%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secret%20to%20this%2C%20he%20says%2C%20were%20the%20oils%20used%20in%20their%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20mother%20would%20heat%20groundnut%20or%20sesame%20oil%2C%20the%20whole%20house%20would%20fill%20up%20with%20the%20aroma%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20heat%20one%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20sesame%20oil%2C%20and%20the%20other%20cooked%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227894%2Fbest-cooking-oil-indian-food-mustard-sunflower-sesame-olive-soybean-healthy-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefined%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20you%20will%20feel%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two.%20It%20also%20tastes%20better%20and%20has%20more%20essence%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Trichy%20resident%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibi%20considers%20himself%20fortunate%2C%20as%20it%20was%20his%20grandfather%20who%20prepared%20these%20wood%20cold-pressed%20oils%20using%20traditional%20stone%20mills.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20used%20to%20do%20this%20work%20back%20in%20the%201960s%20in%20a%20very%20small%20setup%20in%20our%20village.%20Unfortunately%2C%20he%20had%20to%20shut%20the%20business%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%2C%20when%20refined%20oils%20came%20into%20the%20picture.%20I%20wanted%20to%20revive%20the%20work%2C%E2%80