f-involved%20that%20I%20did%20not%20see%20an%20injured%20cow%20by%20the%20road.%20However%2C%20Buttercup%20saw%20the%20cow%20and%20kept%20pulling%20my%20feet%20till%20I%20went%20and%20looked%20at%20her.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20the%20animal%20care%20helpline%20and%20the%20police%20to%20rescue%20the%20cow.%20I%20was%20relieved%20but%20also%20realised%20how%20selfless%20animals%20can%20be.%20Buttercup%20was%20tired%20as%20well%2C%20but%20she%20forgot%20her%20problems%20and%20wanted%20to%20help%20another%20life%20in%20distress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yati%20and%20buttercup%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328587%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYati%20with%20his%20rescue%20dog%20Buttercup.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Yati%20Gaur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20the%20road%20less%20travelled%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20cinematography%20from%20Noida%2C%20Yati%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20masters%2C%20but%20instead%20chose%20to%20work