e%20and%20people%20better.%20I%20also%20enrolled%20in%20a%20class%20during%20the%20lockdown%20to%20practise%20conversing%20in%20the%20language%20twice%20a%20week.%20This%20helped%20me%20develop%20vocabulary%2C%20fluency%20and%20confidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20out%20with%201%2C000%20followers%20in%202018%2C%20her%20Instagram%20page%20has%20over%2070%2C000%20followers%20today.%20She%20also%20has%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20Discord%20server%20to%20teach%20the%20language.%20Her%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20learning%20Malayalam%20fun%2C%20accessible%20and%20easy%20while%20catering%20to%20the%20many%20Malayalis%20who%20are%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20Malayalis%20who%20live%20abroad%20and%20most%20of%20the%20younger%20generation%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20language%20well.%20There%20is%20a%20pride%20that%20people%20associate%20with%20speaking%20English%2C%20which%20unfortunately%20results%20in%20the%20mother%20tongue%20getting%20sidelined.%20My%20page%20is%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20people%20to%20ask%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20Malayalam%20die%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FNMlMdjgE5uk%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnglish%20medium%20education%20is%20becoming%20more%20popular%20in%20India%2C%20causing%20a%20decline%20in%20knowledge%20of%20native%20languages.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Education%2C%20Planning%20and%20Administration%2C%20the%20number%20of%20children%20studying%20in%20English%20medium%20schools%20in%20India%20increased%20by%20273%25%20between%202003%20and%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20leads%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20children%20preferring%20to%20speak%20English%20at%20home%2C%20rather%20than%20their%20mother%20tongue%2C%20Malayalam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deepa%20Manoharan%2C%20a%20Malayalam%20teacher%20who%20runs%20Muthassi%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20school%20for%20the%20language%20with%20her%20sister%20Darshana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20students%20are%20mostly%20people%20staying%20outside%20Kerala.%20All%20of%20them%20study%20English%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20speak%20Malayalam%20at%20home.%20This%20is%20happening%20even%20within%20Kerala%20now%20and%20carries%20a%20hidden%20danger%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249492%2Fpadma-shri-ali-lakshwadeep-manikfan-ship-agriculture-fish-innovation-india-history-ship-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanguage%20being%20lost.%20%3C%2Fa%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20great%20that%20people%20like%20Elizabeth%20are%20helping%20youngsters%20learn%20the%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deepa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20also%20bats%20for%20teaching%20in%20the%20mother%20tongue.%20The%20NEP%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20possible%2C%20the%20medium%20of%20instruction%20until%20at%20least%20Grade%205%2C%20but%20preferably%20till%20Grade%208%20and%20beyond%2C%20is%20to%20be%20the%20home%20language%2Fmother%20tongue%2Flocal%20language%2Fregional%20language.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuthassi%20is%20one%20of%20the%20schools%20that%20Elizabeth%20promotes%20as%20a%20resource%20for%20learning%20Malayalam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hard%20truth%20is%20that%20there%20are%20not%20good%20resources%20available%20to%20learn%20Malayalam.%20Eliza%20has%20done%20a%20commendable%20job%20learning%20the%20language%20being%20an%20American%20teacher%20herself%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Deepa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20is%20soon%20coming%20out%20with%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20book%20called%20%E2%80%98Davina%20Finds%20Her%20Vowels%E2%80%99%2C%20aimed%20at%20diaspora%20Malayalis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20what%20happens%20when%20languages%20are%20ignored%20in%20my%20own%20house.%20My%20brother%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20Serbian%2C%20which%20means%20his%20family%20won%E2%80%99t.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20know%20English%20as%20it%20is%20a%20global%20language%20and%20helps%20if%20you%20go%20abroad.%20But%20the%20same%20respect%20should%20be%20given%20to%20native%20languages.%20They%20are%20the%20true%20way%20to%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Elizabeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20learning%20the%20language%20helped%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304033%2Fmumbai-friends-launch-mann-centre-for-jobs-for-people-with-intellectual-disabilities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econnect%20with%20her%20husband%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in-laws.%20%E2%80%9CArjun%20and%20his%20parents%20speak%20fluent%20English.%20Yet%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20connect%20on%20a%20deeper%20level%20with%20them%20because%20I%20learned%20their%20mother%20tongue.%20It%20really%20makes%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20boy%20Arivazhakan%20in%20June%202023.%20And%20just%20like%20she%20envisioned%2C%20she%20says%20she%20looks%20forward%20to%20giving%20her%20son%20the%20knowledge%20of%20both%20his%20parent%E2